title: The Sims 4 Life & Death: Official Gameplay Trailer
description:
The SimsтДв 4 Life & Death Expansion Pack* arrives Oct 31 and is available for pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack  

Order now through Dec 12 for the Macabre Mementos Digital Content**; the Lasting Legacy Family Portrait, Mournful Melodies Music Box, and Plumed Elegance Mask.

Peel back the veil: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack  

Sims can collect Bucket List goals and earn rewards for completing them тАУ but don't worry if they can't! If a Sim dies with Unfinished Business they can still live(?) their dreams as a Ghost, and still earn rewards. The ultimate reward for completing Bucket Lists and Unfinished Business is Rebirth.

For Sims who want to live life on the dark side there are two new careers; an off-screen Mortician career and an active Reaper career which will let you go work for Grim at his secret office as well as travel to reap souls.

There's a lot of eerie fun to get into off the clock as well. Explore Crypts, build your Thanatlogy skill, collect tarot cards, and even adopt a Pet Crow.

Death affects different Sims in different ways. Create fully custom Grieving Rituals and decorate Caskets and Gravesites according to the wishes of the departed Sim or their loved ones. There are 4 types of grief which Sims may experience depending on their personalities and their relationship to the deceased.

Sims can also prepare for their own deaths in life by creating Wills and deciding who to pass on Heirlooms, assets, and children should they pass away.

The journey doesn't end with death. Sims can continue on as Ghosts and even learn new supernatural powers. Ghosts who are helpful while haunting will earn Goodwill essence while Ghosts who think it's fun to be frightening will earn Fear essence. Both essences can be sold for Simoleans.

Embrace the Macabre (one of 3 new traits!) in Life & Death.

Available October 31 at 10AM PT on EA App PC/Mac, Steam, Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S, PlayStation┬о4, and PlayStation┬о5. Pre-order now: https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack

*Requires The Sims 4 & all game updates. For PC, see minimum system requirements for the pack.

**Conditions and restrictions apply. See https://www.ea.com/games/the-sims/the-sims-4/store/addons/the-sims-4-life-and-death-expansion-pack

ABOUT A QUIET PLACE: THE ROAD AHEAD
A Quiet Place: The Road Ahead is a single-player horror adventure game inspired by the critically acclaimed blockbuster movie franchise that highlights a unique survivor story after an invasion of deadly creatures. In this exclusive spin-off, experience the journey of a young woman who must endure a treacherous apocalypse in the midst of interpersonal family conflicts, all while coming to terms with her own inner fears.
Unnerving Atmosphere -- Experience absolute terror as you strive for silence when hiding from, and sneaking by, horrific creatures who hunt using only sound.
Untold Story -- Embark on a dramatic adventure inspired by the A Quiet Place movie franchise as a young survivor trying to navigate the new, eerily tranquil, post-apocalyptic landscape.
Uncanny Ingenuity -- Discover your own path through the world by observing your environment and leveraging the tools in your surroundings.

A Quiet Place: The Road Ahead features an optional "Microphone Noise Detection" setting where creatures will react to sounds that you make through a connected microphone or headset. Stay silent to survive!

title: New Leviathans & New World; Subnautica 2 Official Reveal + Deep Dive, Everything about Subnautica 2
description:
The wait is OVER, Subnautica 2 has been revealed with new Leviathans, Terrifying creatures, A entirely NEW world and ancient mystery to uncover!

Subnautica 2 is the next game in Unknown WorldsтАЩ beloved open-water survival series. Filled with mystery and wonder, Subnautica 2 will launch in 2025 via Early Access on Steam, Epic Games Store, and Windows Store and via Game Preview on Xbox Series X|S with Xbox Game Pass.
 
In Subnautica 2, players will explore a new alien ocean world rich with vibrant biomes, strange creatures, and hidden secrets. Whether playing with friends or alone, players will craft tools, build custom bases, and navigate the depths of this immersive world as they forge their own survival stories. 

Subnautica 2 will officially introduce multiplayer co-op, offering a new way to experience the adventure with friends. Up to four players will be able to explore the oceanтАЩs vast environments together, and collaborate to craft tools, build bases, and face the challenges of a planet teeming with both beauty and danger.
